Name: COSMO TECH SAS
Description:
SAS & Cosmo Tech

Analytics and digital twin simulations can combine to reveal, optimize, and enable best outcomes. Together, Cosmo Tech and SAS accelerate an organization’s ability to simulate all possible figures and to make better decisions – without requiring specialized IT or data scientist skillsets.


Build living models that recommend the best course of action. Build a virtual representation of your business (Digital Twin) by using a business-friendly interface and perpetually right-size your decisions by incorporating internal and external signals. Creating these models of assets and processes provides other positive effects such as developing action plans that improves business outcomes.

Operate more efficiently to exceed customer and stakeholder expectations. By deploying SAS advanced AI and analytic technologies, paired with Cosmo Tech simulation of possible futures, business leaders can focus on adjusting levers to achieve ESG goals and other business outcomes.

Proactively transform risk into strategic advantages. The landscape of business effectiveness is ever-changing; Our partnership enables revenue growth and market share gain by helping you to leverage AI, IoT, simulations, and synthetic data to uncover insights and actions.


Focus Areas:  Digital Twin, Simulation, Metaverse, Analytics, AI, Machine Learning, Supply Chain, Demand Planning
